To start observing a snap expiration:

* Run sh snap-expire -e {youremail@canonical.com} -a {snap} {snap}
* Copy the contents of ~/snap/surl/common/snap.surl to a new repository secret in
  https://github.com/canonical/snap-expire/settings/secrets/actions.
* Add your run of snap-expire to .github/workflows/ci.yaml.
